&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;YYGad1j5co5mirx53h1lEm7Mg8d&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgACYJVUlUwBct7MjBugqpoe&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative | Production | Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgUP2FJDNRYvelXM5264XIKd&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgWSkc50jChfaUt6JVBoyWJg&quot;&gt;The Creative Strategist is the owner of a pod and is fully accountable for its creative, operational, and performance success.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FbMOd1urJoCI5Mx6Q7Slx57Sg7f&quot;&gt;This role sits at the intersection of creative strategy, social media expertise, production execution, and people leadership. The Creative Strategist sees both the big picture and the smallest details. They are responsible for where the page is going, how it grows, and how the team delivers day to day.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZkHRdDRZuovSKDx1DP3lPlkXgUe&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FqHyd9TmmoRQ6MxnHMFlSf7pgGf&quot;&gt;The need to leave and breathe their channel!&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgGsSPbEs0n38ysi4xF8FKGg&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-doxlgn5z0PtCneRzV7fPM0tQ7zb&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgIHnIE7mj4AfqwsYSBvargc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-list=&quot;number&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;heading-3&quot;&gt;Creative Ownership and Strategy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgrUcexHWvMd5wP0UaMe5RKb&quot;&gt;The Creative Strategist leads the full creative direction for their accounts.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgWySd8ISbOAd6kDKW66H1oe&quot;&gt;This includes:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgHX4TCBN6JZ7Rbv58sMj5ZL&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Translating client goals and direction into a clear creative strategy.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlg40CH8u8C7rJRbLdpOTD3Tf&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Building a long-term content direction, not just individual videos.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgp6D86z0IdJ9PX85ld8GFWc&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Creating structured posting plans that serve a bigger narrative and growth vision.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgMEZDXGXBMi98SYAg3kd9zb&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Understanding storytelling deeply, ensuring every video is compelling, relevant, and clear.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlghkA2lfqhdzgZDKW1DnIerd&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Being the final creative approval for all content before publishing.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxlgkZ6bu0I41ElrIqLUKQUK2c&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Ensuring high creative standards, no mistakes in storytelling, messaging, subtitles, or execution.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/

