&lt;div data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://nas.io/&quot;&gt;Nas.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;is building Shopify for the AI era: a platform that helps net-new entrepreneurs find customers and sell online. We’re an AI-first business platform used by 16,000+ entrepreneurs, growing rapidly month over month, and we scaled revenue 5× in 2025.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Backed by leading Silicon Valley VCs and based in Singapore, we’re entering a critical scale phase.&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;rich-text-paragraph&quot; data-eleid=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;text-only&quot; data-eleid=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Why work with us:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;rich-text-paragraph&quot; data-eleid=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;text-only&quot; data-eleid=&quot;5&quot;&gt;Here, you are not just an employee — you are treated as a true owner of the company. Our CEO shares clear updates on business strategy and operations every week, and your ideas are always welcome. You’ll have direct access to leadership, and strong support to turn great ideas into reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;rich-text-paragraph&quot; data-eleid=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;text-only&quot; data-eleid=&quot;7&quot;&gt;You’ll work alongside a team of highly intelligent, passionate, and execution-driven engineers, using some of the most advanced AI technologies in the industry to solve real problems for users around the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
