&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Bk7ydfr25o1io7xmtq1lSGyTgJe&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Generate high level insights from formative research, market gaps and help drive the business to scale.&lt;/div&gt;
