&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zuscdct6UoJKVoxoK0Gu2sOysQd&quot;&gt;Nas.com is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Backend Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to support and scale our backend systems for a fast-growing creator platform. This is a full-time&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;role open to candidates in Singapore.&amp;nbsp;The ideal candidate thrives in an &lt;strong&gt;asynchronous work environment&lt;/strong&gt;, can work independently, and is passionate about improving product reliability, system architecture, and performance. You will play a key role in ensuring our platform remains robust and responsive around the clock.&lt;/div&gt;
